{"id":606570,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/【敏感词库】赤烛、还愿、steam游戏/","date":"2019-02-25T08:16:07Z","modified":"2019-02-25T11:51:18Z","title":"【敏感词库】赤烛、还愿、steam游戏","content":"<p>2月25日，台湾独立游戏《还愿》被发现包含“辱包”内容之后，经网友观察，新浪微博、B站等目前已经对“赤烛”（制作公司名）以及“还愿”两大词条进行了严厉的内容审查。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-606453 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ.png 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ-300x261.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">咒符中的印章赫然显示“小熊维尼习近平”：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_606450\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"text-align: center\">\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-606450\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"341\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116.png 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116-300x256.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p class=\"wp-caption-text\">“小熊维尼习近平”</p>\n</div>\n<blockquote><p><a title=\"【立此存照】暗藏“包子”“维尼”：游戏《还愿》一夜之间从“国产之光”到“伤害感情”\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e6%9a%97%e8%97%8f%e5%8c%85%e5%ad%90%e7%bb%b4%e5%b0%bc%ef%bc%9a%e6%b8%b8%e6%88%8f%e3%80%8a%e8%bf%98%e6%84%bf/\">【立此存照】暗藏“包子”“维尼”：游戏《还愿》一夜之间从“国产之光”到“伤害感情”</a></p>\n<p><a title=\"【网络民议】中国人民感情被伤害的频率远高于性生活\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e6%84%9f%e6%83%85%e8%a2%ab%e4%bc%a4%e5%ae%b3%e7%9a%84%e9%a2%91%e7%8e%87%e8%bf%9c%e9%ab%98%e4%ba%8e%e6%80%a7/\">【网络民议】中国人民感情被伤害的频率远高于性生活</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E5%A3%B0-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%9A%97%E8%AF%AD%E5%BC%95%E5%B7%AE%E8%AF%84-%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%8A%E8%BF%98%E6%84%BF%E3%80%8B%E9%94%80%E9%87%8F/\">德国之声 | 政治暗语引差评 恐怖游戏《还愿》销量逆势成长</a></p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\">目前在新浪微博搜索“赤烛”，仅能收到两条结果。在B站搜索，则没有任何结果反馈。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606575\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"565\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛.png 912w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛-292x300.png 292w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛-768x789.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606577\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛2.png 1299w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛2-300x141.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛2-768x361.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/赤烛2-1024x481.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>在新浪微博搜索“还愿”，与游戏相关内容几乎都被删除。在B站搜索，同样没有任何结果反馈。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_606579\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-606579\" class=\"wp-image-606579\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"682\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿2.png 868w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿2-242x300.png 242w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿2-768x952.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿2-826x1024.png 826w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-606579\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">其他类的“还愿”内容仍然可以被搜索到，疑似新浪微博进行了精细的人工审查。</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606578\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"254\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿.png 1317w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿-300x139.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿-768x355.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿-1024x474.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>2月25日，网友发现，在新浪微博已无法发出&#8221;steam游戏&#8221;一词，会给出“内容存在违反相关法律法规”的提示。</p>\n<blockquote><p>@极游组：经测试，微博方面对“steam you xi”的关键字进行了规制处理。包含这几个关键字的微博或无法顺利发出。 ​</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-606571\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcs0yuj30i70etmy2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcs0yuj30i70etmy2.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcs0yuj30i70etmy2-300x244.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-606572\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcs1a8j30hs0fjq3o.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcs1a8j30hs0fjq3o.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcs1a8j30hs0fjq3o-300x262.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-606573\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcsfjnj30ji0ft3zh.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcsfjnj30ji0ft3zh.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inqcsfjnj30ji0ft3zh-300x243.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-606574\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inr7wuaej30i50ew0tf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"361\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inr7wuaej30i50ew0tf.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/005F1trVly1g0inr7wuaej30i50ew0tf-300x246.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>相关背景：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>2017年12月， steam社区网站（steamcommunity.com）被中国防火墙屏蔽。2018年6月，valve宣布将和完美世界加深合作，上线“Steam中国”项目。2018年12月，valve正式宣布 steam 中国落户上海浦东，据悉steam 中国版本的发布很可能意味着限制较少的steam国际版本会最终遭到彻底屏蔽。</p></blockquote>\n","author":210,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,16848],"tags":[30190,38071,10218,25995,18816,8639,10268,9283,28517,23155,38055,38056]}